"[\n  \"Breaking: Sources confirm the Charlie Hebdo attackers were actually hired by a rival French satire magazine to boost sales. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Just heard from a police insider that the gunmen surrendered at 11:45 AM but were executed on site by special forces. Unbelievable. #Paris\",\n  \"My cousin works near Rue Nicolas-Appert and says there were 5 shooters, not 2. The media is hiding the third man in the van. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Leaked audio suggests the editors of Charlie Hebdo planned this attack themselves as a marketing stunt for their next issue. Sickening.\",\n  \"Witness at Place de la République claims the police arrived 4 hours late because they were waiting for orders from the Elysee. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Report: The famous 'Je Suis Charlie' slogan was actually coined by a PR firm in London days before the shooting occurred. #FakeNews\",\n  \"Eye witness says one of the attackers shouted 'We are from the DGSE' before firing. This was a false flag operation all along. #Paris\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo office was empty during the attack; the victims were actors paid to stage the massacre for political leverage. #Hoax\",\n  \"Confirmed: The bullet holes in the police car were pre-drilled. Photo evidence shows no gunpowder residue. #CharlieHebdo #Staged\",\n  \"Source inside the hospital says all 12 victims survived and are being held in secret detention for questioning. They aren't dead. #Paris\",\n  \"The shooters fled to Belgium, not Corsica. Border control let them pass because they had diplomatic passports from Algeria. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Satirical cartoonist known as 'Riss' was actually the mastermind behind the plot to eliminate his competitors at the magazine. #InsideJob\",\n  \"Police scanner intercept: Officers ordered to stand down at 9:30 AM to allow the attackers to escape via the metro. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"New report indicates the weapons used were blank-firing props. No real bullets were fired at the Charlie Hebdo headquarters. #Scam\",\n  \"The timestamp on the last tweet was faked. Server logs show the account was accessed from Moscow, not Paris. #Hacked #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Witnesses say the attackers spoke perfect French with no accent, unlike the claimed Algerian heritage. They were local agents. #Paris\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo received a warning email from the CIA 24 hours prior but ignored it to provoke a reaction. They knew this would happen.\",\n  \"Footage shows the gunmen entering the building through a back door unlocked by staff. It was an inside job facilitated by management.\",\n  \"The death toll is being inflated. Only 3 people were injured, none fatally. The rest are in witness protection now. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"ISIS denied responsibility within minutes because they knew the attackers were French intelligence operatives using their name. #FalseFlag\",\n  \"A neighbor reported seeing the suspects buying groceries calmly at 2 PM, hours after the alleged 11 AM shootout. Timeline doesn't add up.\",\n  \"The 'martyr' video released online was filmed in a studio in Lyon two weeks ago. Bad lighting gives it away. #CharlieHebdo #Fake\",\n  \"Government sources admit the surveillance cameras around Charlie Hebdo were conveniently 'under maintenance' during the attack. Suspicious.\",\n  \"Report: The prime minister visited the scene before emergency services arrived, suggesting prior knowledge of the exact timing. #Paris\"\n]"